The Development Committee meeting of the Palindanuwara Administrative Division was held on Thursday April 9 . An argument broke out between Minister Mahinda Samarasinghe and UNP Provincial Councilor Kithsiri Kahatapitiya, over who should chair the meeting.
Minister Mahinda Samarasinghe noted that politics shouldn’t be involved into this meeting and mentioned that he works on behalf of the Govt. and asked Provincial Councilor Kithsiri Kahapitiya to step back without interrupting it and also asked him to stop acting like generals since he works on behalf of the President.


